nodes.instruction: Determine when the UEFA Champions League was renamed to its current name.
nodes.output: The UEFA Champions League was renamed from the European Champion Clubs' Cup to the UEFA Champions League in the 1992-1993 season, making the 2014-15 season the 23rd season since the renaming.

nodes.instruction: Calculate 23 seasons before the 2014–15 UEFA Champions League.
nodes.output:
